\subsection{When to Use This}{

Use Dunn test when:
\itemize{
\item Your Kruskal-Wallis test shows significant differences (p < 0.05)
\item You want to know which specific groups differ
\item Your data violates normality assumptions
\item You have ordinal data or skewed distributions
